Package: blastar
Title: BLAST Analysis and Sequence Tools for R
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Loukas", "Theodosiou", 
           email = "theodosiou@evolbio.mpg.de", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for BLAST analysis, sequence alignment, and phylogenetic 
    tree construction. Integrates with NCBI databases through the 'rentrez' package 
    for sequence retrieval and offers multiple sequence alignment capabilities.
